<li>Toon, Owen B., Alan Robock, Richard P. Turco, Charles Bardeen, Luke Oman, and Georgiy L. Stenchikov, 2007b: <a href="http://climate.envsci.rutgers.edu/pdf/SciencePolicyForumNW.pdf" class="external text" title="http://climate.envsci.rutgers.edu/pdf/SciencePolicyForumNW.pdf" rel="nofollow">Consequences of regional-scale nuclear conflicts.</a> <i>Science</i>, <b>315</b>, 1224-1225.</li>
<li>Toon, Owen B., Alan Robock, Richard P. Turco, 2008: <a href="http://ptonline.aip.org/journals/doc/PHTOAD-ft/vol_61/iss_12/37_1.shtml" class="external text" title="http://ptonline.aip.org/journals/doc/PHTOAD-ft/vol_61/iss_12/37_1.shtml" rel="nofollow">Environmental consequences of nuclear war.</a> <i>Physics Today</i>, December, 37-42.</li>
